The Output module lets you take a stereo audio signal out of your eurorack case and
pass it to other audio gear, an audio interface, speakers, or headphones. It provides a
ballanced line level output and a dedicated stereo headphone output with
independed volume controls for both and a VU meter to measure your output levels.
